{{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = V |image = Consul V.jpeg |species = [[Moebius]] |age = |gender = Male |haircolor = |eyecolor = Red |affiliation = [[Consul]]s |appearances = {{XC3}} |voiceactorjp = Yohei Tadano |voiceactoreng = Charles Dale }} {{Quote|What?! You think I’m some lowly errand boy? Stuff your messages. I’m all about the screaming! And I will enjoy yours before the day is through! That’s why I am Moebius!|V}} '''V''' is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == V is a [[Consul]] who commands [[V's Colony]], his own [[colony]] made up entirely of autonomous [[Levnis]]es. He is callous and greedy, and has a vain and pompous personality without the intelligence to back it up, often making poor decisions.
== Story == It is possible that he is one of the oldest Consuls, as V is seen in flashbacks from at least 1000 years ago. At that time he often used his Blade to execute soldiers who had reached the ends of their tenth terms. One such victim was [[Ashera]]. Another time, the execution was stopped by [[M]], allowing [[Crys]] to send off the soldier in the very first [[Homecoming Ceremony]].
Shortly after [[Colony Lambda]]'s [[Flame Clock]] is broken, he is seen watching the results of a battle with [[R]], with both of them placing bets on the battle. The battle ends in in his favor and he claims his reward as [[N]] looks on in disgust.
During ''[[Side Story: Taion]]'', he detects a signal from the Flame Clock of the abandoned [[Ferronis]] of the [[Lost Colony]]. He attempts to assault the colony using his own colony of Levnises. However, the [[Ouroboros]], led by [[Taion]], outsmart him by repairing the abandoned Ferronis and using it as a distraction in order to circle around the back and attack him by himself. Too shortsighted to recognize the trap, and too hubristic to attempt to retreat, despite being given the option to flee back to Z by Ouroboros, he fights and is killed by the Ouroboros. {{clr}}
== Battle == {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Moebius V |image = Moebius_V.jpg |caption = Moebius V |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Moebius]] |level = 56 |area = [[Erythia Sea]] ([[Farlaine Underpass]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Side Story: Taion]]'' |respawn = No |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = 3,712 |cp = 400 |sp = 0 |gold = 0 |hp = 3,255,000 |strength = 1,208 |healing = 257 |dexterity = 230 |agility = 128 |physdef = -20% |ethdef = 0% |critrate = 0% |guardrate = 0% }} '''Moebius V''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] who is a Moebius fought at level 56 in [[Farlaine Underpass]] in [[Erythia Sea]] during ''[[Side Story: Taion]]''.
=== Resistances === {{XC3 Resistances |break = 75% |topple = 0% |daze = 0% |burst = 0% |launch = 0% |smash = 0% |blowdown = 90% |knockback = 90% |physdebuff = 75% |etherdebuff = 80% }} {{clr}} == Trivia == * Consul V appears to be a homage to [[wikipedia:Vaudeville|vaudeville]] villain stereotypes from the 19th and early 20th centuries; the tubes on his helmet appear similar to a handlebar mustache, the helmet itself is shaped like a top hat, and in the English dub he speaks with an exaggerated accent exemplified by cartoon characters such as [[wikipedia:Dick Dastardly|Dick Dastardly]] and [[wikipedia:Snidely Whiplash|Snidely Whiplash]].
